premise_source_doc_sentence: The remix album My Worlds Acoustic and compilation album My Worlds : The Collection were released later that November ; the latter packaged My World , My World 2.0 , and My Worlds Acoustic into a two-disc set .
The tour was officially announced on March 16 , 2010 , a week before My World 2.0 was released .
It is Bieber 's first concert tour which supports his two-part debut album My World and My World 2.0 .
Upon the release of My World 2.0 in March 2010 , its predecessor peaked at number five .
Upon its release , My World 2.0 received generally favorable reviews from music critics , who complimented its production .
